data.name: textBox13.Value
data.value: = Format("{0:N0}",Fields.dosage) + " " + Fields.unitDesc + " " + Fields.perDay + "x a Day" + " " + IIF(Fields.noDay = "maintenance", "Maintenance", IIf(Fields.noDay = "needed", "As Needed", IIf(Fields.noDay = "single", "Single Dose", Fields.noDay + " Day/s")))

data.name: sqlDataSource2.SelectCommand
data.value: select Measurement.measurementDesc, MedicalPrescription.rxID, MedicalPrescription.personnelID, OutgoingItems.productCode, OutgoingItems.qtyRx, OutgoingItems.dosage, OutgoingItems.perDay, OutgoingItems.noDay, OutgoingItems.note, ProductList.productDesc, Personnel.personnel_lastName, Personnel.personnel_firstName, Personnel.personnel_midInit, Personnel.personnel_extName, ProductUnit.unitDesc, Personnel.title, Personnel.licenseNo from MedicalPrescription LEFT JOIN OutgoingItems on MedicalPrescription.rxID = OutgoingItems.rxID LEFT JOIN ProductList on ProductList.productCode = OutgoingItems.productCode LEFT JOIN Personnel on Personnel.personnelID = MedicalPrescription.personnelID LEFT JOIN ProductUnit on ProductUnit.unitID = ProductList.unitID LEFT JOIN Measurement on Measurement.measurementID = ProductList.measurementID where MedicalPrescription.rxID = @rxID
